{
  "body": "The docs on [Proc](https://docs.perl6.org/type/Proc) have a nice example:\r\n```perl6\r\nmy $p1 = run 'echo', 'Hello, world', :out;\r\nmy $p2 = run 'cat', '-n', :in($p1.out), :out;\r\nsay $p2.out.get;\r\n```\r\n\r\nWe should provide the same thing for [Proc::Async](https://docs.perl6.org/type/Proc::Async).\r\n\r\nSee also: https://irclog.perlgeek.de/perl6/2017-09-25#i_15213849",
